{"tid":1459874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪時候要去海港城shopping 呢","createTime":"2019-08-12T23:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T23:11:29.000Z","uid":270862,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"20924d901fca74e9377daeae345607fa52340572","tid":1459874,"uid":270862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:11:29.000Z","msg":"九倉置業（1997）旗下的商場海港城日前貼出告示，稱「除非有罪惡發生，警察請勿內進」，隨即受多方壓力，九倉（0004）首席顧問、前主席兼前全國政協常委吳光正今日在《信報》發文稱示威者「再出師已無名」，「反送中」的大樹已倒。記者今日走訪九置旗下的海港城及時代廣場，已不見相關告示。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1565610317829&amp;issue=20190812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1565610317829%26issue%3D20190812&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB2zDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=39573676\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1565610317829%26issue%3D20190812&h=1080c43f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1565610317829&amp;issue=20190812</a>"}]}